{"tid":1461700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"白衫警犬啱啱話射布袋彈要瞄住身體最大範圍 但講唔通","createTime":"2019-08-13T09:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:46:48.000Z","uid":257516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f29a4e091766f3e4cf2298e43942b3ba925b37e7","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"白衫警犬啱啱喺記者會話 射布袋彈要瞄住身體最大範圍<br />\n「身體最大範圍」即係頭部以下嘅地方 理應瞄頭唔係 亦唔應該係警犬嘅目標<br />\n當狗係喺遠距離射布袋彈 因為有地心吸力會跌落嚟<br />\n但依家射咗入眼 咁即係100%肯定係瞄頭啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港警察 謀殺市民</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a2ab8752cc8816763a30781bf09ce68a52c69782","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:01:05.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"d4cc6c297d8a6c335469e076338174f367c33d56","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"381e79ef827248250190fc26466f0ae60bfe414f","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"46fd16571bceef01136f495e9bd88bb4fb3580ca","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"2ddfb7fe580891e57aebcacf318698a3fa6d5d08","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:02:38.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"cead3e237e4a8fb695ab7a26477fa74473e166fa","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:02:52.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"ce048f07072026e6bbfe541ac162c0aa6bee07d3","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"1cf6676b2fd0c02143f1ec894f162c29da8d3daf","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:03:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"3b06ec140dff2445ab5568c6c8e83c41038c75b7","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:03:34.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"7e751a2eba0eceb04a3c5ee03315ff9f44044c1a","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:03:53.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bb3d6de662edce870da96ba0a9ef0c6d1d3c0beb","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:04:59.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9abb54b4f2d69da72316b09d906e951766c475a8","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"0"},{"pid":"b6a6c84510dcd299a7fecb502869e843d30159ab","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:05:36.000Z","msg":"唔通又要用老毛語錄推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e7aa77d6437631156bcf1012d3e9f6e4ea0653","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:28:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> <br />\n毛主席 : 被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我認為，對我們來說，一個人，一個黨，一個軍隊，或者一個學校，如若不被敵人反對，那就不好了，那一定是同敵人同流合污了。如若被敵人反對，那就好了，那就證明我們同敵人劃清界線了。如若敵人起勁地反對我們，把我們說得一塌糊塗，一無是處，那就更好了，那就證明我們不但同敵人劃清了界線，而且證明我們的工作是很有成績的了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《被敵人反對是好事而不是壞事》（一九三九年五月二十六日），人民出版社版第二頁"},{"pid":"3874580e21687c798d1a5b2942b4e0c4b5e0d1ce","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。 </span></span><br />\n《和中央社、掃蕩報、新民報三記者的談話》<br />\n（一九三九年九月十六日），《毛澤東選集》二版第二卷第五八零頁"},{"pid":"e0b2f418d92633516d66e7109f705858b07aaafb","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"<em>你要有知識 ! 你就得參加變革現實的實踐。</em><br />\n<br />\n節錄自毛語錄"},{"pid":"bffe76dbc01bca0428ea699884a683bee63061c1","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"<em>星星之火，可以燎原。</em><br />\n<br />\n節錄自毛語錄"},{"pid":"c42016d7aa40cf4928dde5d40d50e060182504db","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">革命不是請客吃飯</span></span>，不是做文章，不是繪畫繡花，不能那樣雅致，那樣從容不迫，&ldquo;文質彬彬&rdquo;，那樣&ldquo;溫良恭儉讓&rdquo;。革命就是暴動，是一個階級推翻一個階級的暴烈的行動。"},{"pid":"86b9bff9a553523fcd3cd94149d1548f4072d394","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:29:50.000Z","msg":"<em>把別人的經驗變成自己的，他的本事就大了。</em><br />\n<br />\n節錄自毛語錄"},{"pid":"7ec99c433d5e1df3742f1c4c62f27b120f3e72b9","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mYYeanC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmYYeanC.png&h=10dcd4bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ceff7d4f691c5f14f3cc2a9aec7147d7c805a7fd","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:30:55.000Z","msg":"<em>歷史是人民創造的。</em><br />\n<br />\n節錄自毛語錄"},{"pid":"1177ca2c4db5f6aff926a5eeffc9ba152de6b1da","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:40:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"696856654c5f87e21cc018de6c0b79fdfa9d636d","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:42:03.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"862849cd97eaf41fcdf9849b82f3fd31784e84e6","tid":1461700,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:42:24.000Z","msg":"9"}]}